org.locationtech.geomesa.redis.data

JedisClusterUncloseable 

class JedisClusterUncloseable extends UnifiedJedis

A subclass of JedisCluster that overrides the close method to prevent closing the cluster connection.

    Override the close method to prevent closing the JedisCluster instance.

    Override the close method to prevent closing the JedisCluster instance. This is intentional to avoid closing the cluster connection.
